# Introduction
This is c++ version of numpy (so called numC)

# Licence
This project is licenced under the terms of GNU General Public Licence v3.0

# Structure
The library will be consist of two classes. Matrix and Vector. 
Vector will be based on Matrix which is nx1 matrix.
They will share all necessary functions.
I will try to use overwriting of functions as many as possible to achive
gneric coding

Error handling code will be defined in Errors.h

Utility functions such as generic print function will be defined in Utils.h

